<p>Petal features a complex button style generator inside the LESS code to make adding new color sets as simple as possible.</p>

<h3 id="section-buttons-basic">Basic Button</h3>
<div class="demo-panel p-15">
  <div class="block">
    <button class="btn">Button</button>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="demo-code">
{{#markdown}}
``` html
<button class="btn"></button>
```
{{/markdown}}
</div>

<p>To make a button, simply add the <code>.btn</code> class, presumably to a <code>&lt;button&gt;</code> or <code>&lt;a&gt;</code> element.</p>

<h4>Button Style Options</h4>
