<p>If you're using the <code>.compact</code> option, you need to apply them to both the actual button and the dropdown caret button.</p>

<h5>Options</h5>
<ul>
  <li><code>data-dropdown-align="right"</code> on <code>ul.dropdown-menu</code> : Align the menu to the right.</li>
