  <li><code>@include-btn-split</code> : set to <code>false</code> if you're not going to use any split buttons in your project. (Split button requires the button dropdown styles, so if you have <code>@include-btn-dropdown</code> set to false, split buttons will not render properly regardless the value of <code>@include-btn-split</code>.)</li>
  <li><code>@btn-disable-colored-dropdown</code> : set to <code>false</code> if you don't want colored dropdown menus. You'll get black-on-white menus regardless of the button color.</li>
</ul>


